# AnimaTweaks Emote System
# Use these commands to trigger emotes:

# Wave emote
# /function emotes/wave
execute as @s run playanimation @s animation.player.emote.wave

# Point emote  
# /function emotes/point
execute as @s run playanimation @s animation.player.emote.point

# Thumbs up emote
# /function emotes/thumbs_up
execute as @s run playanimation @s animation.player.emote.thumbs_up

# Clap emote
# /function emotes/clap
execute as @s run playanimation @s animation.player.emote.clap

# Dance emote
# /function emotes/dance
execute as @s run playanimation @s animation.player.emote.dance 